            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书太美了，另外才知道原来“一丈青”的原型是耳挖型发簪。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="701321494">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-701321494" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-701321494" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="701321494">有用</a>
                </span>
