          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jacintaH/" class=" " title="Jacintta H">Jacintta H</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40569110">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">金银质纽扣，自唐代起即为贵族服饰的组成部分。在古代，纽扣的形制有雌雄的象征，雄者为扣，雌者为纽，相合而成纽扣。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-12-05 13:17</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>金银质纽扣，自唐代起即为贵族服饰的组成部分。在古代，纽扣的形制有雌雄的象征，雄者为扣，雌者为纽，相合而成纽扣。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
